      `= true` assignments), round-trip column-select preservation in GET, model property
      definitions, log lines, or XML-doc comments — none are filter clauses.

      Result independently confirms task 060 inventory §3B and matches task 061's flag that
      "063+064 likely re-scope to verify-empty + escalate maker-side audit". Disposition note
      authored at `projects/spaarke-platform-foundations-r3/notes/task-064-verify-empty.md`
      documenting greps run, per-file categorization, cross-references, and maker-side audit
      escalation path (export `Spaarke` solution → grep `Views/*.xml`, `Workflows/*.xml`,
      `BusinessRules/*.xml`, `PluginAssemblies/*.xml` for `sprk_searchindexed` before the
      eventual drop-old-field step, which is itself deferred beyond R3 per spec FR-3H3.4).

      No code changes; no tests changed; no BFF publish (no `.cs` edits). FR-3H3.4 satisfied
      for in-repo scope; AC-H3.2 satisfied. Sibling task 063 (UI cluster) ran in parallel
      with zero file overlap.
